Dear {AccountId.Name},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!!

Your service request has been successfully logged in our system. Please find the details below for your reference:

Project: {!Opportunity__r.Name}
Unit Number: {!Opportunity__r.RW_Project_Unit__r.Name}
Service Request Number: {!CaseNumber}
Request Category: {!Case_Category__c}
Date Logged: {!CreatedDate}

Our team will review the request and get back to you within 3 business days.

You can track the status and updates of your request on the Runwal Connect App.

If you require any immediate assistance, please feel free to connect with our customer support team.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
